trong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nThe camera is now facing to the side of the craft. Very annoying when flying a plane and your camera is suddenly messed up\u003Cbr\u003E\nThe world is all stars and you are at impossible places (under ground) when timewarp is 0 after quickload\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESteps to Replicate\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nI\u0027ve had 100% replica success:\u003Cbr\u003E\n- Fly. Be it a rocket. Be it a plane\u003Cbr\u003E\n- Quicksave\u003Cbr\u003E\n- Quickload\u003Cbr\u003E\n-\u00A0\u003Cu\u003EBEFORE\u003C/u\u003E\u00A0you\u0027re back in the game, put timewarp to zero. Make sure you hear the timewarp go to zero\u003Cbr\u003E\n- Wait for the game to load\u003Cbr\u003E\n- You have sucessfully managed to get into the void\u003Cbr\u003E\n- Continue time and you\u0027re back where you were, with camera facing the side\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nThe camera also switches angle if you don\u0027t do the timewarp bug. Camera always switches, very annoying.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EFixes / Workarounds (if known..)\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nNone for the camera issue\u003Cbr\u003E\nFor the spawn issue, just continue time\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EA list of ALL mods. \u00A0If the list is long, please consider using a spoiler window.\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nNone\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOther Notes / Screenshots / Log Files (if possible..)\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nImmediately after load (paused during the load)\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022image.png?width=1193\u0026amp;height=671\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 dat